data.text:
DIFRNCE is founded in 2008 in The Netherlands. Starting with MP3 & MP4 players with a big success in Europe.

With our broad assortment of unique designed speakers, portable mp3/mp4 players we offer you the best quality for a very good price.

See & hear the difference.

We can even provide customized and private-label consumer electronics for your retail brand.
